<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Happy Birthday! ✨</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #ffe4e1; /* Soft Pink */
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            color: #d81b60;
        }

        .container {
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 400px;
            margin-top: 50px;
            padding: 20px;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            animation: fadeIn 2s ease-in;
        }

        h1 { font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        
        .photo-placeholder {
            width: 150px;
            height: 150px;
            background: #fce4ec;
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin: 20px auto;
            border: 5px solid #ff80ab;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .letter-box {
            display: none; /* Pehle chhupa hua hoga */
            background: #fff9fb;
            padding: 15px;
            border: 1px dashed #ff80ab;
            margin-top: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .btn {
            background-color: #ff80ab;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-size: 16px;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-top: 20px;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .btn:hover { background-color: #f06292; }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="photo-placeholder">
            <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/150" alt="Birthday Person" style="width:100%;">
        </div>
        
        <h1>Happy Birthday, [Name]! 🎂</h1>
        <p>Today is all about YOU! ✨</p>

        <button class="btn" onclick="showLetter()">Click to Open Letter 💌</button>

        <div id="letter" class="letter-box">
            <p>Pyaari/Pyaare [Name],</p>
            <p>Main bas ye batana chahta hoon ke tum meri life ka sab se haseen hissa ho. Hamesha aise hi muskurate raho! ❤️</p>
            <p><b>Love Always!</b></p>
        </div>
        
        <br>
        <a href="https://open.spotify.com" target="_blank">
            <button class="btn" style="background:#1DB954">Play Our Song 🎵</button>
        </a>
    </div>

    <script>
        function showLetter() {
            var x = document.getElementById("letter");
            x.style.display = "block";
            window.scrollTo(0, document.body.scrollHeight);
        }
    </script>

</body>
</html>
